


Health Information System
A simple, clean, and API-driven health information management system that allows doctors to:

Create health programs (e.g., TB, Malaria, HIV).

Register new clients.

Enroll clients into one or more health programs.

Search and view registered client profiles.

Expose client profiles through a REST API for integration with other systems.

🚀 Features
Create and manage health programs.

Register and manage clients.

Enroll clients into multiple programs.

Search and retrieve client profiles easily.

Expose client profile data securely via an API.

🛠️ Tech Stack
Backend: Python (Flask) OR Node.js (Express)

Database: SQLite (or In-Memory for prototype)

API: RESTful endpoints

Version Control: Git & GitHub

📚 How to Run
Clone the repository:

bash
Copy
Edit
git clone https://github.com/your-username/health-info-system.git
cd health-info-system
