Start the server:

bash
Copy
Edit
python app.py
or

bash
Copy
Edit
npm start
Use Postman or your browser to interact with the API.

📖 API Endpoints
POST /programs — Create a new health program

POST /clients — Register a new client

POST /enroll — Enroll a client into a program

GET /clients — List all clients

GET /client/<id> — View a client's full profile

